757
00:39:41,704 --> 00:39:44,367
if we want to we can

758
00:39:44,367 --> 00:39:46,170
merge those branches together

759
00:39:46,170 --> 00:39:50,054
into basically one shared thing again

760
00:39:50,054 --> 00:39:51,357
And the reason why this

761
00:39:51,357 --> 00:39:53,381
